@SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress = https://localhost:7076

### Slot Machine API Tests

### 1. Create a new user
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "TestPlayer"
}

### 2. Get user by ID
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/id/1

### 3. Get user by username
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/username/TestPlayer

### 4. Get all users
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users

### 5. Add cash to user account
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/1/balance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.0
}

### 6. Add free spins
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/1/free-spins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "count": 5
}

### 7. Check if user can play
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/games/1/can-play

### 8. Spin the slot machine
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/games/1/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "betAmount": 1.0
}

### 9. Get game history
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/games/1/history?limit=20

### 10. Cashout user balance
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/1/cashout

### 11. Get all symbols
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/symbols

### 12. Get symbol statistics
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/symbols/statistics

### 13. Get specific symbol
GET {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/symbols/1

### 14. Update symbol value and weight
PUT {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/symbols/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 0.50,
  "weight": 300
}

### 15. Reset symbols to defaults
POST {{SlotMachineAPI_HostAddress}}/api/symbols/reset-to-defaults